= Nimzowitsch Defence, Williams Variation =
At this point, White can build a large pawn center with [[/3. d4/]]. Black can attempt to control the center with pieces with either [[/3...Bg4/]], allowing 4. d5 Ne5 5. Nxe5, or [[/3...Nf6/]]

